title: Adobe CS3 Master Collection for Windows 30-Day Trial (3-Disk Set
description:
Adobe Creative Suite 3 Master Collection for Windows 30-Day Trial (3-Disk Set)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a set of three disks, two DVDs and one CD.

These are genuine disks from Adobe, bought and paid for with my money,
not somebody&#039;s stolen credit card.

The installation is the 30-day trial.

There is no keygen or activation applet included, because, amongst all the
available downloadable keygens, I couldn&#039;t find a single one that either
(a) wasn&#039;t a virus, and/or (b) worked correctly.

A working, virus-free keygen and activation applet is desperately needed!

A description of each disk can be found in the folder which contains the
image file for that disk.

Hope these images are useful, and that a working, virus-free keygen can be
found soon!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
